üß± Run:AI Limitations ‚Äì MAN-41 & LEW-41 GPU Clusters

Last Updated: November 2025
Owner: Sri Yasaswini Bokka ‚Äì Platform AI Engineering
Scope: MAN-41 (Primary GPU Cluster) | LEW-41 (Secondary GPU Cluster)
Platform Stack: OpenShift 4.x | Run:AI v2.21 | NVIDIA H200 GPUs | Harness CI/CD | JupyterHub


---

üß© 1. Scheduling & GPU Distribution

Limitation	Description	Cluster Impact	Mitigation / Next Steps

Single-Node Confinement	Run:AI cannot automatically distribute one job across multiple GPU nodes without MPI/DDP.	Both clusters ‚Äî large LLM training restricted to 8 GPUs per node.	Enable distributed training (Pytorch DDP / Horovod).
Fractional GPU Fragmentation	0.25/0.5 GPU allocations leave idle VRAM segments unused.	MAN-41 (Dev) shows lower utilization under multi-user queues.	Encourage full-GPU runs for LLM tests or adjust fair-share policy.
Pod Pending State	Scheduler fails to assign GPU due to taints/tolerations or node pool conflicts.	Common in LEW-41 after node restarts.	Verify labels and tolerations; restart Run:AI scheduler pod if stuck.



---

‚öôÔ∏è 2. MIG & Driver Dependencies

Limitation	Description	Cluster Impact	Mitigation

Stale MIG Partitions	MIG instances stay marked ‚Äúin-use‚Äù after pod deletion.	MAN-41 GPU #5 and #6 often require manual reset.	nvidia-smi mig -cgi -C or node reboot before rescheduling.
Version Mismatch Risk	Run:AI Operator ‚Üî CUDA Driver mismatch after updates.	Affects both clusters during 2.21 upgrade.	Maintain Driver‚ÄìOperator compatibility matrix; test in LEW-41 first.



---

üóÇÔ∏è 3. Storage & PVC Lifecycle

Limitation	Description	Impact / Cluster	Mitigation

No Automatic PVC Backup	Run:AI does not retain PVC data for user home dirs or Jupyter pods.	LEW-41 user PVCs lost after namespace cleanup.	Use OpenShift PVC retain policy or NAS snapshot automation.
NAS Mount Mismatch	Path differences (/mnt/data vs /home/jovyan) cause access denied.	Intermittent in MAN-41 Dev.	Standardize Helm templates with /mnt/nas mount.



---

üîê 4. RBAC & Namespace Authorization

Limitation	Description	Impact	Mitigation

RBAC Misalignment	Run:AI roles don‚Äôt fully map to OCP RBAC.	‚ÄúUnauthorized‚Äù error on PVC mount between projects.	Create cluster-level role bindings via LDAP groups.
Manual Role Sync	No auto propagation of Run:AI roles to OCP.	Manual update needed when users added to projects.	Schedule weekly RBAC sync job via Harness.



---

üìä 5. Monitoring & Dashboard Visibility

Limitation	Description	Observed Cluster	Mitigation

Metrics Delay (10-30 s)	GPU utilization and job status refresh delayed in UI.	Both clusters.	Integrate Prometheus / Grafana for real-time metrics.
Pod-Scoped Logging Only	Multi-pod training logs not aggregated under one job.	MAN-41.	Centralize logs with Fluentd or ELK stack.



