üß∞ 6. CI/CD Integration Gaps

Limitation	Description	Impact	Mitigation

Harness Trigger Limitation	Run:AI CLI not natively supported in Harness pipeline.	Manual job trigger required.	Use REST API wrapper in Harness step.
Jupyter Idle GPU Consumption	Notebooks stay active after user logout.	Unused GPU locked in MAN-41.	Deploy idle-pod cleanup cron job.



